<MAP TIMEOUT="" MODE="STANDALONE">
  <COMMENT> Important note: once a transaction is placed in QUEUEDFORDELIVERY status, it can be immediately picked up by another thread, and even delivered and completed before this </COMMENT>
</MAP>

<MAP TIMEOUT="" MODE="STANDALONE">
  <COMMENT> current thread has a chance to even get to its next step - this means that the following call should be nearly immediately followed by a getFirstAvailableQUEDFORDELVTrans call </COMMENT>
</MAP>

<INVOKE TIMEOUT="" SERVICE="fwcore.data.trans:z_updateActiveStatus" VALIDATE-IN="$none" VALIDATE-OUT="$none">
  <COMMENT> QUEUEDFORDELIVERY    Document is queued for delivery </COMMENT>

